    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a683cc3f34d26c8006451119c2a6c25f.poster.avif?t=1768824325\" width=626 height=92 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a683cc3f34d26c8006451119c2a6c25f.webm?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a683cc3f34d26c8006451119c2a6c25f.mp4?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Hive</i> 是一款带有角色扮演元素的即时战略游戏，你将作为昆虫族群的集体意志来指挥蜂巢。在一片庞大而古老的地下世界中，到处都是被遗忘的文明、巨大的生物以及无数隐藏的秘密，你的旅程既是为了生存和进化，也是为了揭开这片失落世界背后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你的殖民地不断扩张，你对散布在新伊甸各处遗迹的理解也会逐渐加深。那些遗迹展现出一段悲剧性的过去，并暗示了更深处的事物。在这个既敌对又瑰丽的环境中，危险与发现始终并存，每一个决策都可能改变你的蜂群命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/8dcb800c59dacdd0a8bf5e04269b5dee.webp?t=1768824325\" width=640 height=40 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演昆虫族群的集体意志，在支离破碎的地下世界中带领蜂群生存与繁荣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/b63cc1684782b395f68b8c389f06b4b8.poster.avif?t=1768824325\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/b63cc1684782b395f68b8c389f06b4b8.webm?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/b63cc1684782b395f68b8c389f06b4b8.mp4?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造并扩展你的地下巢穴，打造蓬勃发展的殖民地和强大的军队。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从被击败的敌人身上采集 DNA，用来解锁新的单位、能力和战术选择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为你的生物装备从远古文明遗迹中回收的强力物品，强化它们在战场上的表现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a850835446000fcbbc5d42fe7f1d8d7b.poster.avif?t=1768824325\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a850835446000fcbbc5d42fe7f1d8d7b.webm?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a850835446000fcbbc5d42fe7f1d8d7b.mp4?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对抗庞大而古老的怪物，根据敌人不断变化的威胁调整你的战略。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验一条贯穿新伊甸地下世界的史诗剧情，这片世界既危险又充满魅力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/82d8da5ab479936d69574ddd60be00e2.poster.avif?t=1768824325\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/82d8da5ab479936d69574ddd60be00e2.webm?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/82d8da5ab479936d69574ddd60be00e2.mp4?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一座既美丽又致命的世界，其中布满远古文明、神秘遗迹和敌意十足的生物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏足风格各异的生物群系，从静谧而繁茂的泉源地区到炽热的火山区域，每一处都有独特而危险的美感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/895b6744dba6ab49bac55a2a7105e568.poster.avif?t=1768824325\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/895b6744dba6ab49bac55a2a7105e568.webm?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/895b6744dba6ab49bac55a2a7105e568.mp4?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
